<div id="deltos">

<h2>δέλτος</h2>

<p>
  <ul>
    <li>Hello, this is Deltos, a one page operating system for work.</li>
    <li>You can focus on your work postively to innovate and create ideas.</li>
    <li>Go diving with a unique sound sequence to focus the mind.</li>
    <li>Drag an image to the window to focus your mind.</li>
    <li>Then type away. All Private. Download a disk to back it up.</li>
    <li>Use the sun clock for daily unique time markers.</li>
  </ul>
</p>

<div id="info">
    <p>Status: <span id="statusMessage">Awaiting Location...</span></p>
    <p>You live at: <span id="coords">--</span></p>
    <p>⧋ <span id="sunAlt">--</span></p>
    <p class="peak">Daily Max Altitude (Noon): <span id="maxAlt">--</span></p>
    <p class="below">Daily Min Altitude (Midnight): <span id="minAlt">--</span></p>
</div>

<div id="canvasContainer">
    <canvas id="sunCanvas" width="400" height="200"></canvas>
</div>

<div id="window">
  window
  <div id="imageWindow">
    drop image here
  </div>
</div>

<div id="mind-bubbles">
  <p>

    <button id="playPauseButton">
      Go Diving
    </button>
  </p>
  <div id="bubblesMessage"></div>
</div>

<div id="notes">
  <p>
    <textarea id="noteTextarea">write private notes and save them here</textarea>

    <div id="previousNotes">
    </div>

    <button class="tiny-link" id="clearNotes">Clear your notes</button>
  </p>

</div>

<div id="disk">
  <div>
<hr>
    Save Disk <button id="backupBtn">Save</button>
<br>

    <label for="uploadFile">Load disk</label>
    <input type="file" id="uploadFile" accept=".json" class="input-file">
    <button id="restoreBtn">Load</button>
  </div>

  <div id="messageBox" class="message-box hidden"></div>
</div>

</div>
